    <text type="letter">
        <body>


            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01856.001.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <!-- Recto of document is postcard filled out to WW. -->
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Meltonsville Ala</name>
                    
                    <date when="1876-08-05">Aug 5 1876</date>
                    
                </dateline>
            </opener>
                <p><address>
                        <addrLine>Walt Whitman</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>431 Stevens St</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Cor West</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Camden</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>New Jersey</addrLine>
                    </address></p>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01856.002.jpg" type="verso"/>

            <p>If all people could derive a practical <hi rend="underline">Theory of Living</hi>,
                from the incident noted <unclear reason="illegible" resp="#nhg" cert="medium">20</unclear> years ago, of the European Nobleman, who being imprisoned solitarily in a <hi
                    rend="underline">dark dungeon</hi>; conquered his <hi rend="underline"
                    >tedium</hi>, by continually throwing away and <hi
                    rend="underline">recovering a lot of brass pins</hi>! How often <hi
                    rend="underline">restlessness</hi> produces <hi rend="underline"
                    >criminality</hi>! How fortunate to leave to be <hi rend="underline"
                    >content</hi> with doing <hi rend="underline">nearly nothing</hi>&#8212;with
                    <gap reason="illegible" extent="3 words"/> My soul, for <hi rend="underline"
                    >twenty</hi>
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="3 words"/>
                <hi rend="underline"><unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nhg"
                        >purturbability</unclear></hi>!"&#8212; <gap reason="illegible"
                    extent="3 words"/>
                <hi rend="underline">remain</hi> gentlemanly <gap reason="illegible"
                    extent="11 words"/></p>
            <closer><signed>J. N. J.</signed></closer>
          
        </body>
    </text>
